// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-0491 — Mass File Rename (ransomexx)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 80afa8d0-3a90-503f-8931-fcd871134627

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
